data.description: Beautifully renovated luxury townhome nestled in a private gated community at the heart of Buckhead, The Gables at Peachtree offers a serene retreat conveniently located between Buckhead and Brookhaven. Within walking distance to premier shopping and dining destinations, this expansive 4000+ sq. ft. townhome boasts a spacious open floor plan that has been meticulously updated. Revel in hardwood flooring throughout, stunning fireplace tile work, and a custom bar featuring white quartz countertops and a new wine refrigerator. The interior has been freshly painted in a neutral white palette, enhancing the airy ambiance.    The townhome features a 2-car garage, an elevator shaft, and a main floor with generously proportioned living spaces, including a gas fireplace, a sizable walk-in bar, and arched built-in bookshelves. A glassed-in room with skylights floods the space with natural light, while the custom kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with a large center island, quartz countertops, high-end appliances, and built-in storage solutions. Upstairs, the owner's suite impresses with a coffered ceiling, a spa-like bath with separate shower and tub, and two separate walk-in closets. A second bedroom/office space with a full bath can be easily converted back to its original design, seamlessly connected to the primary bedroom.    The terrace level offers additional living space, including a large den with fireplace, a generously sized bedroom with walk-in closet, and a second bedroom/office space, all serviced by an updated full bath with double vanity and walk-in shower. The private community features two gated entrances/exits with ample guest parking. Enjoy the convenience of nearby grocery stores, restaurants, and upscale shopping destinations such as Phipps Plaza and easy access to GA-400. This meticulously renovated townhome offers an unparalleled blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience in an unbeatable location.
